metadata.name: Rage Against the system.
metadata.description:
I dont like when they tell me, how to do it. i like to be me, i like to be chaos, i like to be free. I dont wait for gas fees, if im feeling it, im dropping it. I dont like to promo myself. Im a artist, im not a walking marketing billboard. Im done with that ****. And this is all about.
Rage against the system.
